snippet.title: SONG in support of JOHNNY DEPP - Johnny For the Win
snippet.description:
#JusticeforJohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #mentoo

This is a song I wrote in support of Johnny Depp, against the terrible person that is Amber Heard.

It also highlights the trivialization of violence against men in general.

Patreon.
https://www.patreon.com/kingkameleon

Johnny for the win, Johnny for the win
Johnny for the win, Johnny for the win
Johnny for the win, Johnny for the win
Aaaaahhhh

I stand with Johnny, Johnny go
I stand with Johnny, Johnny go
I stand with Johnny, Johnny go
May Justice be heard

Put on your makeup
Push up those good old B cups
You've got it going on

Beat up your husband
Hey women, life is open season
On any man around

But when I saw your face in the news
You literally painted yourself as the victim of...
Abuuuuse

I stand with Johnny, Johnny go
(Johnny for the win, Johnny for the win)
I stand with Johnny, Johnny go
(Johnny for the win, Johnny for the win)
I stand with Johnny, Johnny go

May Justice be heard

They say "you go, girl!"
They say you rule the world
And nothing is your fault
(Nothing at all!)

Whatever your path
Be a big bed-shitting psychopath
We must believe you all

So stunning and brave
When you laughed and said that no one would believe he was...
Abuuuuused

I stand with Johnny, Johnny go
(Johnny for the win, Johnny for the win)
I stand with Johnny, Johnny go
(Johnny for the win, Johnny for the win)
I stand with Johnny, Johnny go

May Justice be heard

Yeah Johnny's got his demons
Deep in the heart
You're number one, he wants you gone

He took it on the chin
While you were trying to win... with
Advantage of vagina joke cards

When you say take it like a man
You're really saying, fuck your pain
We have it easy in your eyes
We get to have more suicides

Solo

We stand with Johnny, Johnny go
(Johnny for the win, Johnny for the win)
We stand with Johnny, Johnny go
(Johnny for the win, Johnny for the win)
We stand with Johnny, Johnny go
(Johnny for the win)

May Justice be heard
